{"type":"message","id":"1419b0a6","parentId":"bec545a5","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:21:36.928Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 18:21 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 搜索企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息。返回格式：每条信息包含标题和简要内容。"}],"timestamp":1774002096926}}
{"type":"message","id":"3cbd65b6","parentId":"1419b0a6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:21:41.142Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为子代理搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态，包括企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等领域，整理3-5条关键信息。\n\n我需要使用web搜索技能来完成这个任务。让我先读取web搜索技能文件。","thinkingSignature":"39363743a2a1734204b53a9068bbb5d7f50fb52f24bdd7ffa85a2aaf4b778eb6"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_euiippa38146_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":108,"output":94,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30537,"totalTokens":30739,"cost":{"input":0.0000324,"output":0.00011279999999999999,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0036644399999999997,"total":0.0038096399999999996}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774002096928}}
{"type":"message","id":"f2cbf7e4","parentId":"3cbd65b6","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:21:41.153Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_euiippa38146_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774002101149}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5e84bbe","parentId":"f2cbf7e4","timestamp":"2026-03-20T10:21:45.395Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要使用这个搜索工具来搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。我将搜索几个关键词来获取相关信息。\n\n让我搜索以下关键词：\n1. 企业数字化转型 2026\n2. 智能安防 行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成 最新技术\n4. IT运维服务 行业发展","thinkingSignature":"74a66149de1f6288bfc2453c84c43ccc93b3eb5c041c7eac946a809bf3c11272"},{"type":"text","text":"我来搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lveootx4jj24_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026 趋势\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lveootx4jj24_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防 行业动态 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lveootx4jj24_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维 行业发展 2026\" --output json","timeout":60}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":821,"output":233,"cacheRead":30433,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31487,"cost":{"input":0.00024629999999999997,"output":0.00027959999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0009129899999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00143889}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774002101153}}
